  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "The training was performed by establishing skip connections for each estimated location to acquire features from other scales, thereby alleviating overfitting.",
    "They also used dot products and softmax to obtain weighted multiscale features and optimized these features to highlight the characteristics of traffic signs and improve the ability to detect traffic signs in complex backgrounds.",
    "Traffic sign detection is a popular research area within the Faster R-CNN algorithm model.",
    "Traffic sign detection and recognition is an important part of visual perception algorithms to recognize and understand traffic signs in real-world road scenes in real time, thus facilitating correct decision-making and precise motion control of intelligent vehicles.Reference [31] introduced a new module, the Attention Network (AN), into Faster R-CNN.",
    "This module was used to identify all potential Regions of Interest (ROIs)."
  ],
